N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4223.5 - Unfilled races

State Regulations

The racing secretary may, in the event a stake or
handicap does not fill, replace such race with an overnight race carrying a
guaranteed purse consistent with the daily average purse. Notes
